text: Tried their fried fish spinach soup with fried noodle at $5.70. Full bowl of spinach and minced meat with egg and goji berry. Soup base is sweet and tasty. Stall owner is very polite and friendly. Overall 9.5/10
Top notch service and importantly, the food is really tasty! Not just worth the try, but to become a regular customer. 5 stars and 2 thumbs up!!
